{
    "type": "refactor",
    "subject": "Replace isRequired() with isValid() in FormComponent.validate()",
    "body": "The method `validate()` in the class `FormComponent` checks if the input is required and if the converted input is null before checking if the input is valid. This order of checks may lead to different behavior if the input is required but not provided or if the input is valid but the converted input is null. The replacement changes this order, checking if the input is required and if the converted input is null before checking if the input is valid. This may lead to different behavior if the input is required but not provided or if the input is valid but the converted input is null.\n\nThis commit replaces `isRequired()` with `isValid()` in line 1027 of jdk-1.4/wicket/src/main/java/org/apache/wicket/markup/html/form/FormComponent.java."
